+## [2026-07-11T00:00:00Z] daemon — health-recoverable auto-retry of parked markers
+
+**Action:** Extended `Hive::Daemon::StaleAgentHealer` with a new, narrower recovery class: two dependency-outage terminal `ERROR` reasons that are only cleared+rerun once a health probe verifies the external dependency is healthy again. Distinct from the existing agent-loss/timeout/limits recovery (clear-and-hope, budget 3, no backoff).
+
+**Scope (v1 allowlist, on by default):**
+- `implementer_failed` — only when the marker/log carries a recognized Codex auth-401 signature AND `codex login status` + a tiny `codex exec` smoke test pass.
+- `claude_launch_failed` — only when the launcher wrapper exists, the ready-detector self-check passes, the claude CLI meets its min version, and `hive doctor` is green.
+- Everything else (generic `implementer_failed`, other reasons) stays parked.
+
+**Mechanics:** probe-before-clear; a universal in-process `hive doctor` gate runs first; retries gated behind a changed health-signal fingerprint + a 2-retry cap with immediate-then-30-min backoff; a safety guard refuses to retry when a terminal success is present, the execute worktree is dirty with non-residue (user) work, git status is unresolvable, or a brainstorm/plan artifact already holds authored content (default-unsafe on any ambiguity). Clearing reuses `Markers.clear_current` + the existing `requeue_plan_rerun` for 3-plan — no new resume path. In-memory budgets/fingerprints reset on daemon restart, consistent with the existing `@error_auto_recoveries` design.
+
+**Config:** global kill-switch `daemon.auto_retry.enabled` (default `true`, validated boolean). Per-reason limits/backoff are hardcoded constants for v1.
+
+**Audit:** `auto_retry_cleared` / `auto_retry_skipped` / `auto_retry_exhausted` to the daemon log (with fingerprint, probe check results, attempt count) and compact `auto_retry_cleared` / `auto_retry_skipped` records to the task `events.jsonl`. Negative decisions throttled per recovery key; exhaustion logged once per process.
+
+**Code:**
+- `lib/hive/daemon/probe_command.rb` (new) — timeout-bounded, process-group-killing command runner; never raises.
+- `lib/hive/daemon/recovery_signatures.rb` (new) — deterministic codex-401 / claude-launch classifiers.
+- `lib/hive/daemon/health_probes.rb` (new) — doctor gate, codex/claude probes, per-tick `ProbeCache`, `health_fingerprint`.
+- `lib/hive/daemon/stale_agent_healer.rb` — `heal_dependency_recovery` path + safety guard + audit; `auto_retry_enabled:` / `health_probes:` / `config_resolver:` seams.
+- `lib/hive/daemon/dispatcher.rb` — resolves the kill-switch and passes a fresh per-tick `ProbeCache` into `heal`.
+- `lib/hive/config.rb`, `config.example.yml` — `daemon.auto_retry.enabled`.
+- `lib/hive/events.rb`, `lib/hive/daemon/logger.rb` — new event types.
+
+**Validation:**
+- `ruby -Itest -Ilib test/unit/daemon/{probe_command,recovery_signatures,health_probes}_test.rb`
+- `ruby -Itest -Ilib test/integration/daemon_auto_retry_test.rb`
+- Full daemon + config + events suite (864 runs) green.
