+## [2026-07-11T12:00:00Z] daemon — auto-retry review-fix pass (git-spam gate + fail-safe logging)
+
+**Action:** Review fix pass 2 on `Hive::Daemon::StaleAgentHealer` health-recoverable auto-retry. Closes the last per-tick `git status` spam hole and tightens fail-safe observability.
+
+**Fixes:**
+- **Persistently-unsafe worktree no longer re-shells `git status` every tick.** The unsafe safety-guard return in `attempt_dependency_recovery` now records `@auto_retry_last_probe_at`/`@auto_retry_last_fingerprint` before returning (mirroring the unhealthy-probe path), so an unchanged environment short-circuits at the cheap re-probe gate and runs `git status` at most once per backoff window. Previously a marker that was unsafe from its first eligible tick never recorded a fingerprint, so the re-probe gate never engaged and git was probed on every tick. Corrected the now-accurate "settled marker no longer spams git" comment.
+- **`auto_retry_artifact_has_content?` no longer green-lights a clobber on a transient read error.** Split `ENOENT` (missing artifact ⇒ safe, no content) from other `SystemCallError` (ambiguous ⇒ treat as authored content, unsafe, + log), matching `auto_retry_git_porcelain`'s fail-to-unsafe stance.
+- **`auto_retry_safe?` outer rescue is now diagnosable.** Fail-safe direction unchanged (any error ⇒ unsafe), but a persistent internal bug now logs `marker_heal_failed` (throttled per project/slug/stage) instead of being silent.
+- **Clarity rename:** the two internal-error throttle maps are `@auto_retry_error_signature_by_task_stage` and `@auto_retry_git_error_signature_by_worktree`, no longer sharing the `@auto_retry_last_*` prefix (whose family is keyed by the 4-arity `auto_retry_key`).
+- **Doc-only:** documented that `heal_dependency_recovery`'s `rescue ⇒ true` is safe only because `AUTO_RETRY_REASONS` is disjoint from the generic agent-loss path; documented `HealthProbes#note_probe_error`'s last-resort logger swallow and `codex_auth_path`'s degraded-fingerprint fallback; corrected `ProbeCommand#drain_ready`'s "spurious wakeup; loop" comment (it falls through, does not loop).
+
+**Tests added** (`test/integration/daemon_auto_retry_test.rb`):
+- unsafe worktree does not re-probe git within the backoff window (git status runs ≤1 across ticks);
+- positive `AUTO_RETRY_SAFE_RESIDUE` allowlist case (`.done` / `result.json` / `.claude/settings.json`-only ⇒ still clears);
+- fail-closed git probe (git failure ⇒ unsafe, logged);
+- bare-`401` trust boundary both directions (marker message ⇒ eligible; log-tail-only ⇒ ineligible);
+- 30-min backoff gate exercised directly (fingerprint gate held open by a changed fingerprint).
+
+**Validation:** `ruby -Itest -Ilib test/integration/daemon_auto_retry_test.rb` (19 runs green); `test/unit/daemon/{health_probes,probe_command,stale_agent_healer}_test.rb` + `test/integration/daemon_stale_agent_healing_test.rb` green.
